  <title>In vitro control of plant pathogenic Xanthomonas spp. using Poncirus trifoliata Rafin</title>
  <URL>https://cn.bing.com/academic/profile?id=d1350910047e1c9e9767b7364270187d&amp;encoded=0&amp;v=paper_preview&amp;mkt=zh-cn</URL>
